name: Gregory Shane KINNARD Jr., Petitioner v. Honorable Michael A. GEORGE, President Judge of the 51st District Court of Adams County, Respondents

parties: Gregory Shane KINNARD Jr., Petitioner v. Honorable Michael A. GEORGE, President Judge of the 51st District Court of Adams County, Respondents.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 8th day of December, 2015, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Quo Warranto is DENIED. The Protho-notary is DIRECTED to strike the name of the jurist from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
